class_data.docstring:
Linux-specific subclass of Hardware.  Defines memory and CPU facts:
- memfree_mb
- memtotal_mb
- swapfree_mb
- swaptotal_mb
- processor (a list)
- processor_cores
- processor_count

In addition, it also defines number of DMI facts and device facts.
